job.body:
Total vacancies:34

Name of the Posts:

  • Post Graduate Teacher (PGT)
  • Trained Graduate Teacher (TGT)
  • Primary Teacher (PRT)
  • Librarian
  • Security Supervisor/ Adm Supervisor

Description

New Central Government Jobs have been published by Army Public School for the vacancies of Post Graduate Teacher. If you are finding a government job in Telangana then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for these vacancies in Telangana, from 19.05.2021, and till 05.06.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Telangana and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about application fee

Educational qualification to apply for department Post Graduate Teacher vacancies in Telangana:

  • To apply for a Post Graduate Teacher vacancies in Telangana, your Bachelor’s Degree, Master’s Degree, B.Ed must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply for these vacancies is 19.05.2021.
  •  The last date to apply for these vacancies is 05.06.2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 57 years old. 

Army Public School Post Graduate Teacher Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Telangana Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for Army Public School PGT, TGT Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process for these vacancies in Telangana. Fill in your details and submit it

  • Or follow all the steps given below,
  •  First, go to the official website of Army Public School and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked BY Army Public School
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
